               <provenance>Walatta Māryām is mentioned as the
                     commissioner (ʾaṣḥafiha) on 38ra. Furthermore her
                     name and the names of her father Gabra Solomon, her mother Walatta Giyorgis and
                     her sister Walatta Mikāʾel are written in supplication formulas. In addition,
                     several other persons are mentioned: Walatta Yoḥannǝs (9rb), Ḫiruta Śǝllāse (12vb), Walda
                     ʾƎsṭifānos (12rb, 38ra), Walatta Tǝnśāʾe (13ra), Gabra Māryām (16rb), Walda Māryām (16rb, 19ra),
                     Ḫāyla Māryām (19ra-rb), Ḫarägä Wäyn (19rb), Tawalda Madḫǝn (38ra, 41vb), ʾabuna Ḫāyla Māryām
                        (42ra).</provenance></history>
